AJLK-02 EMBROIDERED POLY CHIFFON 3 PCS

By Pcs: 3 Pcs Shirt: Poly Chiffon Trouser: Malai Dupatta: Poly Net Fabric composition: Blended Color: Teal

This enchanting teal ensemble, adorned with intricate embroidery, is like a vision of beauty. Its vibrant hue will capture the imagination of any child, making them feel like a star. The heavily embroidered shirt with a stunning neckline makes it a perfect choice for a festive occasion. The matching trousers and flowing dupatta complete the look perfectly.
